{"tha-ap505:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap505:0.2":"Kanikaravagga ","tha-ap505:0.3":"3 Kasumaraphaliyattheraapadana ","tha-ap505:1.1":"“Kanikaramva jotantam, ","tha-ap505:1.2":"nisinnam pabbatantare; ","tha-ap505:1.3":"Addasam virajam buddham, ","tha-ap505:1.4":"lokajettham narasabham. ","tha-ap505:2.1":"Pasannacitto sumano, ","tha-ap505:2.2":"sire katvana anjalim; ","tha-ap505:2.3":"Kasumarikamadaya, ","tha-ap505:2.4":"buddhasetthassadasaham. ","tha-ap505:3.1":"Ekatimse ito kappe, ","tha-ap505:3.2":"yam phalam adadim tada; ","tha-ap505:3.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap505:3.4":"phaladanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap505:4.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap505:4.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap505:4.3":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap505:5.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap505:5.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap505:5.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap505:6.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap505:6.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap505:6.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap505:7.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma kasumaraphaliyo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap505:8.1":"Kasumaraphaliyattherassapadanam tatiyam. "}